CsvTemplate
===========

ActionView::TemplateHandler for csv templates.

Requires the fastercsv gem.

Example
=======

in views/something/data.csv.csv:

  csv << ['Header 1', 'Header 2']

  @data.each do |d|
    csv << [d.id, d.name]
  end

